## 封装加载图片的promise  
```js
let loadImg = (src)=>{
    return new Promise((resolve, reject)=>{
        // write your code here
    })
}
```

questions_answer:
```js
let loadImg = (src)=>{
    return new Promise((resolve, reject)=>{
        let img = new Image();
        img.onload = ()=>{
            resolve(img);
        }
        img.onerror = ()=>{
            reject(new Error());
        }
    })
}
```
